msgid "THRESHOLD"
msgstr "臨界點"

#. ~ Description for THRESHOLD
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Adds mutant professions and scenarios"
msgstr "添加突變職業與場景"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Genetically Unstable"
msgstr "基因不穩定"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Genetically Unstable'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your DNA has been damaged in a way that causes you to continually develop "
"more mutations."
msgstr "你的DNA受損，導致你持續產生更多突變。"

